<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7518986>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pachyrhynchus species, dorsal habitus. A: Pachyrhynchus forsteni male (Morotai); B: Pachyrhynchus viridis (West Papua). Pachyrhynchus species, endophallus in lateral view. C: Pachyrhynchus forsteni (Halmahera); D: Pachyrhynchus morotaiensis (Morotai); E: Pachyrhynchus viridis (West Papua); F: Pantorhytes biplagiatus (Papua New Guinea). Red arrow indicates the dorsal median diverticulum in Pachyrhynchus, and the ventral median one in Pantorhytes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7518986/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

